Package: iccat.pub.maps
Type: Package
Title: ICCAT public maps libraries
Version: 0.1.1
Author: ICCAT Secretariat
Maintainer: Fabio Fiorellato <fabio.fiorellato@iccat.int>
Description: A set of functions and constants to support the production of *static* maps of the Atlantic ocean, including ICCAT sub-areas / stock areas / sampling areas and regular grids.
    This library does not require access to the ICCAT databases (which are private) if not to update (at build time, and if explicitly required) the embedded reference data of ICCAT areas etc. 
License: TBD
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    iccat.pub.aes,
    iccat.pub.data,
    ggplot2,
    ggthemes,
    ggnewscale,
    colorspace,
    scales,
    sf,
    maps,
    mapdata,
    mapplots,
    scatterpie,
    R (>= 2.10)
